{"tid":2270392,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"輕度弱智清潔工涉管有廁所清潔劑 早前被判監八個月 今上訴得直 當庭釋放","createTime":"2020-11-04T04:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T09:58:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":635,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"f636fbc1b51194f00a6307a6586fa6dde32485ce","tid":2270392,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:22:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10953&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=79f3cb75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10953</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院三樓一庭<br />\n#李運騰法官<br />\n<br />\n👤李(32) #不服刑罰上訴 (#20200122屯門 管有攻擊性武器;於6月12日被判處8個月監禁)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n案情：於1月22日在屯門河田輕鐵站的公眾地方無合法權限或合理辯解，攜有攻擊性武器，即一樽鹽酸及一支雷射筆<br />\n<br />\n‼️判處十二個月監禁，認罪扣減後至八個月。被告獲保釋等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n速報：被告當場釋放"},{"pid":"d37b8696fb11b0751b6ece630e1a8c1e0cca3308","tid":2270392,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cb92aea01be2c1d15f8d8b80156527621f5ab4","tid":2270392,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1301e8d14fc28947a297258190c9c75cc871085b","tid":2270392,"uid":240362,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"邵家臻 <br />\n發仔之前承認在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，辯方求情指發仔有輕度智障，惟署理主任裁判官指輕度智障並非減刑理由，判處發仔入獄八個月，幸最終獲准保釋等候上訴。今天就是上訴日，得就冇事，唔得就即時收監，天可憐見，請大家集氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/148053572047302/posts/1528170117368967/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F148053572047302%2Fposts%2F1528170117368967%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=3455c595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/148053572047302/posts/1528170117368967/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"2d490fc23eb0baa884465e99e2d7f0fda6bbd661","tid":2270392,"uid":50891,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"好消息呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a6522e46f3974cc90b40ef4dd3d0be5821d94f","tid":2270392,"uid":230530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"DOJ 會否上訴"},{"pid":"531311e54760bb997998d6f2bea7e61668501627","tid":2270392,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97cb92aea01be2c1d15f8d8b80156527621f5ab4","tid":2270392,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013441d6e475998311ddb4a30f019e5a32be793b","tid":2270392,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d37b8696fb11b0751b6ece630e1a8c1e0cca3308","tid":2270392,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\