uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"Cctoy手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ace3563a066e35a6a0377b10efd92ca8af8cda","tid":2270392,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"智商只得11歲的輕度智障清潔工，今年1月在屯門警署附近被搜出廁所清潔劑、石油氣及雷射筆，他早前承認一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，遭裁判官張潔宜判囚八個月。他不服刑罰上訴，案件今於高等法院進行聆訊。李運騰法官考慮所有因素，亦考慮到清潔工早前案件於屯門裁判法院開審已被還押四個半月，繼續服刑或會影響更生，相信即使駁回上訴他亦只需坐牢不足一個月，最終批准其刑期上訴，即時釋放，書面判詞將擇日頒布。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻議員在庭外代表上訴人發言指，李已有最壞打算，法庭現判其上訴得直「令佢安心左好多」，而今日最重要的是能推翻早前裁判官所指輕度智障並非減刑理由的論點，「弱智係一個求情理由黎架，依樣野好重要」，相信是次上訴得直對日後案例會有深遠影響。"},{"pid":"82ca0eb8cfa439b088c3f82ecdc59e12b270c054","tid":2270392,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddc464e5adaf982fb8c44429fe58eac6e926c14e","tid":2270392,"uid":120807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9176cc8505226ce724514dbe785591b2589672","tid":2270392,"uid":179414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ad0afc66e3f929b577b05f6920cf2ace3fdad8","tid":2270392,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"弱智都搞真係反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2942ae35cb5df6639221cf2f00d68e8de17cda88","tid":2270392,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390b165f3531d4b2bdd1a8652a4ee00aa1e8